44
00:02:43,279 --> 00:02:45,600
Jadi, ayahmu kurang sehat.

45
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,880
Aku paham suasana hatimu sekarang.

46
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,919
Jika ayahmu tidak ada,

47
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,320
