48
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:58,960
Mungkin musuh.

49
00:02:59,279 --> 00:03:01,080
Yaitu orang yang membuatmu
masuk ke sini.

50
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:04,119
Mungkin.

51
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:08,199
