74
00:04:09,519 --> 00:04:11,160
Tentu saja serius.

75
00:04:11,279 --> 00:04:12,959
Ibu bersiaplah dengan baik.

76
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,359
Datang ke Shanghai dua hari lagi.

77
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,239
Direktur Wei.

78
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,559
Hai, aku Lin.

79
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:26,119
