Fanlu.

144
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:28,039
Ayah, kenapa baru pulang?

145
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,640
Direktur Jiang.

146
00:09:31,239 --> 00:09:32,159
Fanlu.

147
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,840
