223
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,640
Ayah sangat senang.

224
00:13:49,239 --> 00:13:51,159
Kau adalah putri kesayangan ayah.

225
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,200
Ayah selalu berharap…

226
00:13:53,599 --> 00:13:56,520
